Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:13.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}摔了一跤 擦破了皮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:20.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}滲出了血 隱隱作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:25.65,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}別擔心啦 很快就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:31.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}明天就會結上層痂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:37.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}從海角邊 開出葉舟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:43.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}張開風帆 隨風而行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:49.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}我自現在 離開土地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}向著七海之遼前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:02.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}習習南風 愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:08.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}轉眼之間 大雨滂沱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:14.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}春之氣息 飄來鼻尖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:20.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}還得趕緊收衣服呢
